```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant DS as Data Scientist
    participant SF as Step Functions
    participant FS as Feature Store
    participant SM as SageMaker Training
    participant MR as Model Registry
    participant EP as Endpoint
    participant MM as Model Monitor

    DS->>SF: Trigger training pipeline
    SF->>FS: Fetch training features
    FS-->>SF: Return feature dataset
    SF->>SM: Start training job
    SM->>SM: Train model
    SM-->>SF: Training complete
    SF->>MR: Register model version
    MR-->>SF: Model registered
    
    alt Auto-deploy enabled
        SF->>EP: Deploy to staging
        EP-->>SF: Deployment complete
        SF->>MM: Enable monitoring
    end

    DS->>MR: Approve model
    MR->>EP: Deploy to production
    EP->>MM: Start monitoring
    MM-->>DS: Performance alerts
```
